definitions.definition: The monetary unit of Russia , Belarus and Transnistria equal to 100 kopeks (Russian: копе́йка ( kopéjka ) , Belarusian: капе́йка ( kapjéjka ) ). The Russian ruble's symbol is ₽ .

main_definition: The monetary unit of Russia , Belarus and Transnistria equal to 100 kopeks (Russian: копе́йка ( kopéjka ) , Belarusian: капе́йка ( kapjéjka ) ). The Russian ruble's symbol is ₽ .
